    {
      "type": "text",
      "title": "A Clean but Vibrant Look",
      "text": "The challenge was to create a black-and-white brand that respects their history but also feels energetic. This is how we chose the color palette. When combined with the \"Link\" symbol, we can create many different shapes and frames to show the connections SaaShock helps build.",
      "variant": "dark",
      "padding": "compact"
    },
